  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Several case report showed that the co-infection of Mycoplasma pneumoniae in patients with
      pulmonary tuberculosis. The aim of this study is to elucidate the prevalence and its clinical
      significance of co-infection of Mycoplasma pneumonia in patients with newly diagnosed
      pulmonary tuberculosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
